Boating
Andalamala's Boating Program
Sky Diving. CA-1, Mill Valley, CA, USA. Dileep Scuba Diving program. Take a thrilling ride over, around, and under the water on this high-speed Chicken Boat adventure. Take a safety briefing, put on a life-vest and set off at full speed in a jet-style boat across the waters near Vila Olimpica. At a moment’s notice, the boat suddenly makes a 360-degree turn before intentionally dipping the tip of boat under water and soaking passengers. Thrilling high-speed boat tour with fast, 360-degree spins Agile boat that dips front-end underwater refreshing passengers Safety briefing and life-vests included Showers available after tour
